missionEventData.data2: Open Galaxy is in active development. The following missions have been included to show off the current features of the game but are not finished.

missionEventData.data1: Vanguard, this is the Victory Star Destroyer Repulse.  Requesting clearance to return to the fleet at Thyferra. We're transmiting our clearance code now.
No response. Vanguard, this is the Victory Star Destroyer Repulse. Requesting clearance to return to the fleet at Thyferra. Lower your gravity wells.
Stay vigilant Alpha Squadron. I'm going to run a registry check on the Vanguard.
Sir, the Vanguard was captured eight months ago. That's a rebel ship!
We don't have time for a fight. Reinforcements will be here any moment. Alpha Squadron take out those E-Wings, while we try to push past the Vanguard.
All hands. Emergency stations. Prepare for combat.
We were pulled out of hyperspace by that Interdictor. It must be guarding the frontier. Her IFF is reading Vanguard. I've definitelly heard of her.
Alpha Squadron. We can't leave this system while the Vanguard's gravity well projectors are active. Take them out!
Acknowledged Repulse. Alpha Squadron activate targeting computers. Focus on the Vanguard's gravity well projectors.
